Title: Giovanna Signature Women's Lace Trimmed 2-Layer Sweep White Dress

Made with virtual silk twill fabric, trimmed with see-through lace on the cuff, neckline and the sweep of the dress, this dress is accented with 2 layers of hem. Versatile and beautiful, you can wear this dress to any occasion including party, special event or church!Fully lined, back zipper closure, dress length from center back is 48 - 49". Hats are sold separately.
